{"id":530615,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fernando_Arrabal","text":"Fernando Arrabal Ter\u00E1n (born August 11, 1932) is a Spanish playwright, screenwriter, movie director, novelist and poet. Arrabal was born in Melilla, Spain, but settled in France in 1955. He calls himself \"desterrado\", which means \"half-expatriate, half-exiled\".\nIn 1962, Arrabal co-founded the Panic Movement with Alejandro Jodorowsky and Roland Topor. It was inspired by the god Pan. He was elected Transcendent Satrap of the Coll\u00E8ge de Pataphysique in 1990.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Spanish_people","surface_form":"Spanish","offset":51},{"uri":"Playwright","surface_form":"playwright","offset":59},{"uri":"Screenwriter","surface_form":"screenwriter","offset":71},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"movie director","offset":85},{"uri":"Novelist","surface_form":"novelist","offset":101},{"uri":"Poet","surface_form":"poet","offset":114},{"uri":"Melilla","surface_form":"Melilla","offset":140},{"uri":"Spain","surface_form":"Spain","offset":149},{"uri":"France","surface_form":"France","offset":171},{"uri":"Expatriate","surface_form":"expatriate","offset":236},{"uri":"Exile","surface_form":"exile","offset":253},{"uri":"Panic_Movement","surface_form":"Panic Movement","offset":294},{"uri":"Alejandro_Jodorowsky","surface_form":"Alejandro Jodorowsky","offset":314},{"uri":"Roland_Topor","surface_form":"Roland Topor","offset":339},{"uri":"Pan_(mythology)","surface_form":"Pan","offset":380},{"uri":"Transcendent_Satrap","surface_form":"Transcendent Satrap","offset":400},{"uri":"Pataphysics","surface_form":"Pataphysique","offset":438}]}